---
import MainLayout from "../../layouts/MainLayout.astro";

const title = "One Piece Card Game Ban & Limited List";
const description = "Official One Piece Card Game banned, limited, and banned-pair list with effective dates and card references.";
---

<MainLayout title={title} description={description}>
	<section class="hero">
		<div class="container">
			<span class="hero-badge">Banlist</span>
			<h1>One Piece Card Game Ban & Limited List</h1>
			<p>
				Official policy notes and the current list of banned, limited, and banned-pair cards. This page
				presents the announcement content in a clean, readable format for competitive play.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="list-section">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="banlist-meta">
				<div>
					<h2>Banned/Limited Card List</h2>
					<p class="meta-date">Announcement date: March 31, 2026</p>
					<p class="meta-date">Publication date: April 1, 2026</p>
					<p class="meta-date">Applies from: April 10, 2026</p>
				</div>
				<div class="banlist-note">
					<p>
						Decks may include up to four copies of a card with the same card number, but some cards are
						designated as banned, banned pairs, or limited for official and sanctioned tournaments.
					</p>
					<p>
						The official list can be revised over time. Cards listed as banned, banned pairs, or limited may
						be removed from the list in a future update as the game environment changes.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="list-section">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>Policy for Ban & Limited Revisions</h2>
			<p>
				The official development team states that a core design goal is to let players enjoy a wide variety of
				decks built around Leader cards. Throughout the year, the environment is monitored to maintain
				strategic diversity, with ongoing evaluation of whether a revision to the ban/limited list is needed.
			</p>
			<p>
				When deciding whether to add cards, the announcement cites multiple factors, including a deck’s win
				rate, performance in major tournaments, usage rate, expected impact on future environments, and whether
				it reduces the viability of other Leaders.
			</p>
			<p>
				The same policy also considers removing cards from the list when the environment allows it, so players
				can enjoy the full range of the game again.
			</p>
			<p>
				Revisions are generally announced twice per year: after the end of Championship Season 1 in Japan, and
				after the World Championship. However, if a card directly compromises a healthy environment, additions
				can be made without waiting for the end of a Championship season.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="list-section">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>Banned Pair (Effective April 10, 2026)</h2>
			<p class="section-note">
				If a deck contains Card A, it is not allowed to include Card B.
			</p>
			<div class="pair-grid pair-grid-plus">
				<div class="pair-card">
					<div class="pair-label">Card A</div>
					<div class="card-visual">
						<button
							class="card-thumb card-thumb-sm"
							type="button"
							data-card-preview
							data-full="/Cards/OP07/OP07-115.jpg"
							data-name="OP07-115 I Re-Quasar Helllp!!"
						>
							<img loading="lazy" src="/Cards/OP07/OP07-115.jpg" alt="OP07-115 I Re-Quasar Helllp!!" />
						</button>
						<div class="card-caption">
							<strong>OP07-115</strong> I Re-Quasar Helllp!!
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="pair-plus" aria-hidden="true">+</div>
				<div class="pair-card">
					<div class="pair-label">Card B</div>
					<div class="card-visual">
						<button
							class="card-thumb card-thumb-sm"
							type="button"
							data-card-preview
							data-full="/Cards/EB04/EB04-058.jpg"
							data-name="EB04-058 Borsalino"
						>
							<img loading="lazy" src="/Cards/EB04/EB04-058.jpg" alt="EB04-058 Borsalino" />
						</button>
						<div class="card-caption">
							<strong>EB04-058</strong> Borsalino <span>(including parallel versions)</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="list-section">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>Previously Banned / Limited Cards</h2>
			<div>
				<h3>Banned Cards</h3>
				<div class="cards-grid">
					<div class="card-visual">
						<button
							class="card-thumb"
							type="button"
							data-card-preview
							data-full="/Cards/OP06/OP06-047.png"
							data-name="OP06-047 Charlotte Pudding"
						>
							<img loading="lazy" src="/Cards/OP06/OP06-047.png" alt="OP06-047 Charlotte Pudding" />
						</button>
						<div class="card-caption"><strong>OP06-047</strong> Charlotte Pudding</div>
					</div>
					<div class="card-visual">
						<button
							class="card-thumb"
							type="button"
							data-card-preview
							data-full="/Cards/OP03/OP03-040.png"
							data-name="OP03-040 Nami"
						>
							<img loading="lazy" src="/Cards/OP03/OP03-040.png" alt="OP03-040 Nami" />
						</button>
						<div class="card-caption"><strong>OP03-040</strong> Nami</div>
					</div>
					<div class="card-visual">
						<button
							class="card-thumb"
							type="button"
							data-card-preview
							data-full="/Cards/OP06/OP06-086.png"
							data-name="OP06-086 Gecko Moria"
						>
							<img loading="lazy" src="/Cards/OP06/OP06-086.png" alt="OP06-086 Gecko Moria" />
						</button>
						<div class="card-caption"><strong>OP06-086</strong> Gecko Moria</div>
					</div>
					<div class="card-visual">
						<button
							class="card-thumb"
							type="button"
							data-card-preview
							data-full="/Cards/ST10/ST10-001.png"
							data-name="ST10-001 Trafalgar Law"
						>
							<img loading="lazy" src="/Cards/ST10/ST10-001.png" alt="ST10-001 Trafalgar Law" />
						</button>
						<div class="card-caption"><strong>ST10-001</strong> Trafalgar Law</div>
					</div>
					<div class="card-visual">
						<button
							class="card-thumb"
							type="button"
							data-card-preview
							data-full="/Cards/OP06/OP06-116.png"
							data-name="OP06-116 Reject"
						>
							<img loading="lazy" src="/Cards/OP06/OP06-116.png" alt="OP06-116 Reject" />
						</button>
						<div class="card-caption"><strong>OP06-116</strong> Reject</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="limited-block">
				<h3>Limited Cards</h3>
				<p class="section-note">No cards are currently limited.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="list-section">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>Previously Banned Pairs</h2>
			<p class="section-note">
				If a deck contains Card A, it is not allowed to include Card B.
			</p>
			<div class="pair-grid pair-grid-plus">
				<div class="pair-card">
					<div class="pair-label">Card A</div>
					<div class="card-visual">
						<button
							class="card-thumb card-thumb-sm"
							type="button"
							data-card-preview
							data-full="/Cards/OP11/OP11-040.jpg"
							data-name="OP11-040 Monkey D. Luffy"
						>
							<img loading="lazy" src="/Cards/OP11/OP11-040.jpg" alt="OP11-040 Monkey D. Luffy" />
						</button>
						<div class="card-caption"><strong>OP11-040</strong> Monkey D. Luffy</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="pair-plus" aria-hidden="true">+</div>
				<div class="pair-card">
					<div class="pair-label">Card B Options</div>
					<div class="pair-b-options">
						<div class="card-visual">
							<button
								class="card-thumb card-thumb-sm"
								type="button"
								data-card-preview
								data-full="/Cards/OP11/OP11-067.jpg"
								data-name="OP11-067 Charlotte Katakuri"
							>
								<img loading="lazy" src="/Cards/OP11/OP11-067.jpg" alt="OP11-067 Charlotte Katakuri" />
							</button>
							<div class="card-caption"><strong>OP11-067</strong> Charlotte Katakuri</div>
						</div>
						<div class="card-visual">
							<button
								class="card-thumb card-thumb-sm"
								type="button"
								data-card-preview
								data-full="/Cards/OP08/OP08-069.png"
								data-name="OP08-069 Charlotte Linlin"
							>
								<img loading="lazy" src="/Cards/OP08/OP08-069.png" alt="OP08-069 Charlotte Linlin" />
							</button>
							<div class="card-caption"><strong>OP08-069</strong> Charlotte Linlin</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<div class="card-modal" data-modal aria-hidden="true">
		<div class="card-modal-inner" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-label="Card preview">
			<button class="modal-close" type="button" data-close>Close</button>
			<img src="" alt="" data-modal-image />
		</div>
	</div>
</MainLayout>

<script>
	window.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
		const previewButtons = document.querySelectorAll("[data-card-preview]");
		const modal = document.querySelector("[data-modal]");
		const modalImage = document.querySelector("[data-modal-image]");
		const closeButton = document.querySelector("[data-close]");

		const openModal = (button) => {
			if (!modal || !modalImage) return;
			const full = button.getAttribute("data-full");
			const name = button.getAttribute("data-name") || "Card preview";
			modalImage.setAttribute("src", full);
			modalImage.setAttribute("alt", name);
			modal.classList.add("is-open");
			modal.setAttribute("aria-hidden", "false");
		};

		const closeModal = () => {
			if (!modal) return;
			modal.classList.remove("is-open");
			modal.setAttribute("aria-hidden", "true");
		};

		previewButtons.forEach((button) => {
			button.addEventListener("click", () => openModal(button));
		});

		closeButton?.addEventListener("click", closeModal);
		modal?.addEventListener("click", (event) => {
			if (event.target === modal) closeModal();
		});
		window.addEventListener("keydown", (event) => {
			if (event.key === "Escape") closeModal();
		});
	});
</script>

<style>
	.banlist-meta {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: minmax(220px, 1fr) minmax(280px, 1.4fr);
		gap: 2rem;
		align-items: start;
	}

	.meta-date {
		margin: 0.15rem 0;
		color: var(--text-300);
		font-size: 0.95rem;
	}

	.banlist-note {
		background: rgba(14, 18, 30, 0.7);
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		border-radius: var(--radius-md);
		padding: 1.2rem 1.4rem;
	}

	.section-note {
		color: var(--text-300);
	}

	.pair-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
	}

	.pair-grid-plus {
		grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) auto minmax(0, 1fr);
		align-items: center;
	}

	.pair-plus {
		width: 54px;
		height: 54px;
		border-radius: 999px;
		display: grid;
		place-items: center;
		font-size: 2.1rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: #0b0f1a;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 107, 61, 0.95), rgba(255, 159, 26, 0.95));
		box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
	}

	.pair-card {
		background: rgba(12, 17, 30, 0.9);
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		border-radius: var(--radius-md);
		padding: 1.2rem;
		display: grid;
		gap: 1rem;
	}

	.pair-b-options {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(140px, 1fr));
		gap: 1rem;
	}

	.pair-label {
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 1px;
		color: var(--accent);
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.cards-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(130px, 1fr));
		gap: 1.2rem;
		margin-top: 1rem;
	}

	.card-visual {
		display: grid;
		gap: 0.6rem;
		align-items: start;
	}

	.card-thumb {
		width: 100%;
		max-width: 170px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		border-radius: 12px;
		border: none;
		background: transparent;
		padding: 0;
		cursor: pointer;
		transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
	}

	.card-thumb:hover,
	.card-thumb:focus-visible {
		transform: translateY(-4px);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow);
		outline: none;
	}

	.card-thumb img {
		width: 100%;
		max-width: 100%;
		margin: 0 auto;
		border-radius: 12px;
		display: block;
		box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
	}

	.card-thumb-sm img {
		max-width: 130px;
	}

	.card-thumb-sm {
		max-width: 150px;
	}

	.card-caption {
		color: var(--text-200);
		font-size: 0.92rem;
	}

	.card-caption span {
		color: var(--text-300);
		font-size: 0.85rem;
	}

	.limited-block {
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		padding-top: 1.2rem;
		border-top: 1px solid rgba(31, 42, 60, 0.6);
	}

	.card-modal {
		position: fixed;
		inset: 0;
		background: rgba(6, 8, 14, 0.85);
		display: none;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		padding: 2rem;
		z-index: 40;
	}

	.card-modal.is-open {
		display: flex;
	}

	.card-modal-inner {
		max-width: min(520px, 90vw);
		max-height: 90vh;
		background: rgba(10, 14, 24, 0.9);
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
		padding: 1rem 1rem 1.5rem;
		position: relative;
		box-shadow: var(--shadow);
	}

	.card-modal-inner img {
		width: 100%;
		max-height: 80vh;
		object-fit: contain;
	}

	.modal-close {
		position: absolute;
		top: 0.75rem;
		right: 0.75rem;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		color: var(--text-100);
		border-radius: 999px;
		padding: 0.35rem 0.8rem;
		cursor: pointer;
		font-size: 0.85rem;
	}

	@media (max-width: 900px) {
		.banlist-meta {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.pair-grid-plus {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.pair-plus {
			margin: 0 auto;
		}
	}
</style>
